MasterChef Canada - Season 3, Episode 1




Yes, No, Maybe So

In the Season 3 premiere, 40 gifted home cooks from across the country audition for Michael Bonacini, Alvin Leung, and Claudio Aprile with their signature dish. With the home cooks requiring a 'yes' from each judge to receive an apron this season, it's harder than ever for finalists to make it into the coveted Top 14. Those who get a 'no' from each judge will be sent home, while those who earn at least one 'yes' will have a second chance, and the opportunity to cook again for a White Apron and a place in the coveted Top 14.




Original Air Date: 14-Feb-2016
